skins.selfIntroduction: I am Denver, fourth ship of the Cleveland-class light cruisers. I fought hard alongside my sisters in the Battle of Empress Augusta Bay. Though I still lack experience, I won't let you down, Commander!
skins.acquisition: Hello! I'm Denver, 4th Cleveland-class cruiser and Knight of the sea! Before I officially start working for you, I've got one question: what is the future you want to see?
skins.login: Welcome back, Commander! Today's a fine day to sortie!
skins.details: Commander, what do you do for your own training? Why don't you come join us down here every now and then?
skins.secretaryIdle1: I want to fight alongside my sisters again, just like at Augusta Bay.
skins.secretaryIdle2: I want to be able to dominate the battlefield with swagger, just like Cleveland.
skins.secretaryIdle3: Even though many of my younger sisters were converted into light aircraft carriers, I'm not jealous of them at all. After all, it's best to be yourself.
skins.secretaryTouch: How strange, Commander, you're also a fan of the "bro fist?" I thought we were the only ones who used that greeting.
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: Commander, what are you trying to feel for?
